---
---
<section id="about" class="py-section-padding-desktop px-gutter max-w-container-max mx-auto reveal">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-headline-lg" style="color:var(--color-on-surface);margin-bottom:2rem">About Me</h2>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;color:var(--color-on-surface-variant)">
        <p class="text-body-lg">I am a passionate Full Stack Web & Mobile Developer dedicated to building modern, scalable, and user-focused digital solutions. My journey started with a curiosity for technology and grew into a commitment to creating impactful applications.</p>
        <p class="text-body-lg">I specialize in developing complete web and mobile experiences, from designing responsive user interfaces to building powerful backend systems. With expertise in technologies such as Laravel, React, Flutter, and modern databases, I focus on delivering applications that are efficient, reliable, and easy to use.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.5rem">
      {[
        { icon: 'school',    color: 'var(--color-primary)',   title: 'Education',  desc: 'Graduate of SMKN 1 Cimahi, majoring in Software Engineering (RPL).' },
        { icon: 'work',     color: 'var(--color-secondary)', title: 'Experience', desc: 'Internship at PT Delta Solusi Internet.' },
      ].map(c => (
        <div class="glass-card" style="padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style={`color:${c.color};margin-bottom:1rem;display:block;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1`}>{c.icon}</span>
          <h3 style="font-weight:700;color:var(--color-on-surface);margin-bottom:0.5rem">{c.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-body-md" style="color:var(--color-on-surface-variant)">{c.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid { display: grid; gap: 3rem; }
  @media (min-width: 768px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: start; } }
</style>
